comments: I rated every category based on teaching ability except easiness.
Not the most amazing TA, but he\'s most certainly a piece of eye candy

Horrible teacher. Still hasn\'t put up our grades after saying he would have them up on Monday... the Wednesday... ridiculous. When I went to the review for the final, all of the other students knew everything because they had good TAs. HE SUCKS! DO NOT TAKE HIM HE IS HORRIBLE AND WILL JUST MAKE YOUR LIFE HELL!

He gives quizzes every section and they are based off the reading. They SUCK! He goes in and chooses the most insignificant detail and puts it on the quiz to "make sure you are reading." He is horrible. People actually read and still got horrible grades on the quiz. Highly advise choosing a different section.
